Text.val: -- Author: Stephan Huppertz
29.04.2013 JH SCR18105 Removed external flag
31.08.2011 GB SCR16716 Added update the CCRY302_TYPEOFDUNNING value from the original country
15.04.2010 GB SCR15449 Added new condition if CLIENT_COUNTRY row does not exist
and extend the program with the new fields in CCRY
First the program must check if the CCRY row exists with DEBC_ADMNO / DEBC_CLNTN
If this row exists (so rct.CCRY_Exists = true) then the program can stop becaus
the required CCRY row already exists
If rct.CCRY_Exists = false and CLNT212_FCI = 2 then the program must check
if CCRY row exists with CLNT104_LEGAL_ADMNO/CLNT104_LEGAL_CLNTNO
If this row exists (so rct.CCRY_Exists(legal) = true) then add a new CCRY row
where all details except admno/clntno can be taken from the CCRY row
with CLNT104_LEGAL_ADMNO/CLNT104_LEGAL_CLNTNO and stop the program
If rct.CCRY_Exists = false and rct.CCRY_Exists(legal) = false then select CCRY
where CCRY308_ADMNO = DEBC_ADMNOCCRY308_CLNTNO = DEBC_CLNTNOCCRY308_COUNTRY
select CTRY_COUNTRY from CTRY where CTRY_COMMISSIONGROUP = V.COMMISSIONGROUP
max CCRY601_COMMISSIONPERC
@ See special Sort: Descending CCRY601_COMMISSIONPERC to fetch CCRY
with max CCRY601_COMMISSIONPERC
-- Only if a client country row exists for the group, create a new one where
CCRY_COUNTRY has to be set to DEBH_HADR_COUNTRY
(R.S. is only performed if a CCRY row exists for the group, so no additional
test required to create a new CCRY row)
